# Build outputs — regenerated inside the image.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/node_modules/
src/Servicedesk.Web/dist/

# Git metadata is not needed in the image (MinVer uses APP_VERSION build-arg
# when running under Docker — see Dockerfile).
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
.vs/
.idea/

# Dev-only secrets and local env. Production reads from /etc/servicedesk/secrets.env
# mounted via compose; nothing in the repo should contain real credentials.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/secrets.json
**/user-secrets/

# OS + editor cruft.
*.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.log
**/*.user

# Test artifacts.
TestResults/
coverage/
*.trx

# Internal docs that must never ship in an image (see CLAUDE.md "Docs — two tracks").
CLAUDE.md
ARCHITECTURE.md
ROADMAP.md
CHANGELOG.md
CHANGELOG-archive.md
docs/

# Plans and memory never belong in a container.
.claude/
